channel.title: Java/DeltaScape help needed
channel.description:
I'm using a DeltaScape source, and it works fine on my computer.
The problem is i've recently bought a VPS from Xlhost (operating system Windows 2003), and when I run.bat on the VPS I get the following error.
The CMD window flashes up for less than a second, showing this error;
[code]Error occured during initialization of VM java/lang/NoClassDefFoundError: java/lang/Object[/code]
I have tried very hard to fix this, but have had no luck as of so far.
Edit: I've noticed I have some rep++ to use, so whoever helps me fix this I will rep++. ;)
Thanks alot for your time, - RuneX -[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 13, 2009, 09:27:35 am[/size][hr]No replies! :eek:
This must be a hard error....
- RuneX -
